{"tid":811563,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗村屋失竊值50萬高達模型　60歲女房東被捕","createTime":"2018-09-09T02:43:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-09T04:21:54.000Z","uid":41404,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"121537f94d730f87d3e1decb6f558766147b56a0","tid":811563,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T02:43:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180909/photo/bkn-20180909052002100-0909_00822_001_01b.jpg?20180909103109\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180909%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180909052002100-0909_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20180909103109&h=27b984dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n櫃上放有多個手辦模型公仔。(趙瑞麟攝)<br />\n<br />\n元朗大旗嶺一間村屋發生爆竊案，昨日(8日)晚上8時許，一名姓陳(45歲)男子報案，指其租住的村屋鐵閘被撬開，有財物失去。警員到場調查，經陳初步點算，報稱失去約25袋、總值約50萬港元的珍藏模型，部分是動畫《機動戰士高達》系列的模型，警方暫列爆竊案處理。警方經進一步調查，懷疑姓馬(60歲)女房東與案有關，遂將她拘捕，由元朗警區刑事調查隊跟進，正調查案中內情。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180909/bkn-20180909052002100-0909_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180909%2Fbkn-20180909052002100-0909_00822_001.html&d=Zdays%2Fva7Gj8FXNPFS381ROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=290ebe69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180909/bkn-20180909052002100-0909_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"0e11833211526d930d2f74612351e70696c8c62b","tid":811563,"uid":150912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T03:29:41.000Z","msg":"個房東可能掉撚左"},{"pid":"c0439490447935dd59bc506452cf5d8b725bfeeb","tid":811563,"uid":81340,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T03:36:34.000Z","msg":"會唔會租霸玩野<br />\n個業主唔識遊戲規則爆入去清場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d4da6efcea7ad31bad23319a23464d1fe758177","tid":811563,"uid":50935,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T